              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two Si(Au) detectors were placed at +-10",
                "degree to monitor the current quality. A detector",
                "array including 7 Si(Au) surface-barrier detectors,",
                "with an interval of 10 degree, was mounted on a",
                "rotatable arm in the reaction chamber to detect",
                "scattering particles at -20 deg to 140 deg."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MAGSP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The Q3D magnetic spectrometer coupled with a",
                "multilayer position-sensitive focal plane gas",
                "detector was employed to select and detect the exited",
                "transfer products."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SIBAR",
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " In order to detect the transfer",
                "products in the range of backward angles, three delta",
                "E-E Si(Au) telescopes were fixed at the backward",
                "angles of 150., 160., and 170. degree in laboratory",
                "system in the reaction chamber."
              ]
            }
